headline: MAA Announces Date of Second Quarter Earnings Release, Conference Call
summary: MAA (NYSE: MAA) announced today that the Company expects to release its second quarter 2025 results on Wednesday, July 30, 2025, after market close and will hold a conference call on Thursday, July 31, 2025, at 9:00 a.m. Central Time. During the conference call, company officers will review second quarter performance and conduct a question-and-answer session.
